OL,4,Cmother and daughter in Boxing Day crash
OL,6,FA driver who killed a mother and her
OL,7,Fdaughter in a Boxing Day crash in
OL,8,FBirmingham has been jailed for 13
OL,9,Fyears and three months.
OL,11,FBirmingham Crown Court was told the 25-
OL,12,Fyear-old was racing another car and
OL,13,Fovertaking at up to 84mph through a
OL,14,Ftraffic-light controlled junction in a
OL,15,F30mph zone, when he lost control of
OL,16,Fhis BMW and crashed into a car
OL,17,Fcarrying four generations of the same
OL,18,Ffamily.
