OL,3,CDriver jailed for 13 years for killing
OL,4,Cmother and daughter in Boxing Day crash
OL,6,FAmanda Riley, 49, and her mother Linda
OL,7,FPhilips, 72, both died at the scene
OL,8,Fdespite the efforts of paramedics to
OL,9,Fsave them at the roadside in Shard End.
OL,11,FOther family members travelling in the
OL,12,FMG suffered injuries, including a
OL,13,Fbroken leg, fractured sternum and
OL,14,Fbruising to the lungs.
OL,16,FThe court were told that both cars
OL,17,Fcaught fire in the aftermath of the
OL,18,Fcrash and that a passerby courageously
OL,19,Fhelped three people in the MG escape.
