OL,6,FDescribing the circumstances of the
OL,7,Fcrash at Ibrahim's sentencing hearing,
OL,8,Fprosecutor Philip Vollans said the
OL,9,Fvictims were travelling home from
OL,10,Ffamily celebrations on the evening of
OL,11,FTuesday, December 26, 2023.
OL,13,FHe said that Ibrahim was racing
OL,14,Fanother BMW before he crashed into a
OL,15,Fquad bike and then hit an MG car,
OL,16,Fcarrying the victims.
OL,18,F"Both (BMW) cars were speeding, both
OL,19,Fcars racing each other.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
