OL,6,F"The defendant was the faster driver
OL,7,Fof the two".
OL,9,FMr Vollans estimated that Ibrahim was
OL,10,Fspeeding for at least half a mile
OL,11,Fbefore the crash, reaching speeds of
OL,12,Fmore than 80mph.
OL,14,FMr Vollans added that the defendant
OL,15,Fhad initially hit a quad bike, which
OL,16,Fhad run a red light and lost control
OL,17,Fwhile in the wrong lane.
