OL,6,FIbrahim, of Old College Road in
OL,7,FSheldon, hit the kerb of the central
OL,8,Freservation and crashed into the
OL,9,Ffamily's car which was on the opposite
OL,10,Fcarriageway.
OL,12,FThe driver's seat of the MG was
OL,13,Fknocked out of its fixings and caught
OL,14,Ffire, leaving its occupants trapped as
OL,15,Fa member of the public attempted to
OL,16,Ffree them.
