OL,6,FA witness saw Ibrahim saying "I need
OL,7,Fto go", whilst lying on the ground
OL,8,Fnear the driver's side of the BMW
OL,9,Fbefore he left the scene. It's thought
OL,10,FIbrahim's car was also on fire
OL,11,Ffollowing the crash.
OL,13,FThe court heard that Ibrahim was
OL,14,Fcaught on camera at Heartlands
OL,15,FHospital where he was treated for a
OL,16,Fleg injury.
OL,18,FHe later returned to the scene where
OL,19,Fhe was arrested, but refused a breath
OL,20,Ftest.
