OL,6,FMr Vollans said: "Both cars were
OL,7,Fcompletely destroyed as a result of
OL,8,Fthis collision".
OL,10,FThree relatives of the victims,
OL,11,Fincluding the driver of the car, read
OL,12,Fvictim impact statements.
OL,14,FOne described those killed as having
OL,15,F"died fighting for their lives, lying
OL,16,Fon a cold roadside, scared and in
OL,17,Ftremendous pain".
