OL,6,FIn a statement read to the court by Mr
OL,7,FVollans, George Philips, husband of
OL,8,FLinda who died in the collision, said:
OL,9,F"Our family are the centre of our
OL,10,Fworld. The aftermath was the complete
OL,11,Fdevastation of my family.
OL,13,F"My wife and daughter both died. My
OL,14,Fworld fell apart. I felt an immense
OL,15,Femptiness."
OL,17,FAmanda and Linda were described to the
OL,18,Fcourt as being hard-working, family
OL,19,Fmotivated and would help anyone.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
