OL,6,FDefence barrister Jasvir Mann,
OL,7,Fmitigating, told the court that
OL,8,FIbrahim has no previous convictions
OL,9,Fand there was strong evidence that he
OL,10,F"led a thoroughly-positive life".
OL,12,FMr Mann said "My instructions are that
OL,13,Fhe has no meaningful memory of that
OL,14,Fday".
OL,16,FThe actions of the quad bike rider,
OL,17,Fwho also left the scene and has never
OL,18,Fbeen identified, had contributed to
OL,19,Fwhat happened he added.
